_sText:
Hello to all!
Today with you I(RuCamper) and last version of a map 35hp_dust!

It became one of the first maps and developed in a current of 2 years (2010-2012).
The first version has been created in far 2010, and it looked awfully enough... :)
![http://img214.imageshack.us/img214/659/22776642.png](http://img214.imageshack.us/img214/659/22776642.png "http://img214.imageshack.us/img214/659/22776642.png")
But in due course I studied did various maps, trained. After I have made a map with the name 35hp_dusty_city_brc and after it has ruined the beta test. I have started to study deeply mapping, my knowledge didn't suffice for creation of a good map. After any new opening for myself, I have solved: it is necessary to make the following version. So has appeared 35hp_dust_2011:
![http://img812.imageshack.us/img812/2827/18165686.png](http://img812.imageshack.us/img812/2827/18165686.png "http://img812.imageshack.us/img812/2827/18165686.png")
Since map creation 35hp_dust_2011 I have learned much, have understood. Also has tried to make all top-level, and here it... 35hp_dust_2012! ![http://img841.imageshack.us/img841/3739/22067249.png](http://img841.imageshack.us/img841/3739/22067249.png "http://img841.imageshack.us/img841/3739/22067249.png")
